Bobby Duncum Jr. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobby_Duncum_Jr. 0 Bobby Edward Duncum (August 26, 1965 – January 24, 2000) was an American professional wrestler. He was best known for his stint in World Championship Wrestling as a member of The West Texas Rednecks.
